Douyin Downloader is a '''cross-platform''' download tool for Douyin videos, built with '''Tauri'''. It provides a simple and efficient way to download videos from Douyin, a popular Chinese social media platform. The tool is available for '''Windows''', '''MacOS''', and '''Linux''' operating systems.

== Overview ==
The Douyin Downloader is a '''free''' and '''open-source''' software that allows users to download Douyin videos with ease. It is built using '''Tauri''', a framework for building '''cross-platform''' desktop applications. The tool has a simple and intuitive interface, making it easy for users to download their favorite Douyin videos.

=== Features ===
The Douyin Downloader has several key features, including:
* '''Cross-platform''' support: The tool is available for '''Windows''', '''MacOS''', and '''Linux''' operating systems.
* '''Easy to use''': The tool has a simple and intuitive interface, making it easy for users to download Douyin videos.
* '''Fast download speeds''': The tool allows for fast download speeds, making it quick and easy to download videos.

== Installation ==
To install the Douyin Downloader, users can download the latest release from the [GitHub repository](https://github.com/lzdyes/douyin-downloader/releases). The tool supports '''Windows x64''', '''Linux x86_64''', and '''macOS 10.13+'''. Alternatively, users can build the tool themselves from the source code.

=== System Requirements ===
To run the Douyin Downloader, users will need to have the following system requirements:
* '''Windows''': '''Webview2''' installed
* '''MacOS''': '''macOS 10.13+'''
* '''Linux''': '''Linux x86_64'''

